args: What's up, Fleur? You look like\nsomethin's bothering you.
I'm still wracking my brains about\nthe art I want to make.
I've been living in this castle for a while\nnow, but I'm just not getting any ideas.

How am I supposed to go about making
something that combines human and
sylvan culture? It sounded simple in
my head...
Hmm... Well, I'm no art buffâ€”
But maybe you could start by collaborating\nwith a bunch'a different people?
Like, say...RANZAL!\nGive the girl a hand!
Wha?! *cough* *wheeze* \nDon't surprise a guy when he's eatin'!
Huh? You sure ya got the right guy?
She's tryin' to work out how to make\nart that mixes in human culture, but\nshe's hit a bit of creative block.
So, you know...two heads, yeah?\nYou guys can just riff off each other,\ndraw up some stuffâ€”you'll be golden.
Well hell, I ain't got anywhere else to be.
Why not? Let's get to it, girlie.
You sure ya don't want someone else\nfer this?
Yep! You're human, and that's all\nthat matters.
So, what is art to you?
Ya know, I've never really thought\nabout that.
But there's really only one answer, yeah?
I'm sorry, I just... I don't understand how\nmuscles can be art.
How can they NOT be?! Here, I'll break\nit down for ya. Artists take their work\nreal serious, yeah?
Well, so do I! Wouldn't be much of a\nmerc if I couldn't swing my weapon\nor wrestle a bear.
I need muscles for all that. MUSCLES!\nBig and bulgy and tighter than shrunken\nundies.
Ah, I see! You worked at it, and honed \nyour craft, so I guess that kinda does\nmake it art, huh?
Hmm... So if I use your muscles for a\npainting, would that make it fusion art?
What, ya want me to model for ya?
Finally, someone with EYES!\nSure girlie, count me in.
Great! But first I need a favor.
She tells me to wait in the courtyard and\nthen just up and vanishes...
Guess she's plannin' to paint me\noutside? I should think up some\nawesome poses...
Huh? What's that ya got there?
I needed to gather materials. See?\nI got a bucket, some paints, and a\nbiiiiig piece of paper.
Whoa. Didn't realize we were goin'\nso big.
Well, the paper's GOT to be big!
How else are you gonna dive onto it?
Sure, I getcha. Gotta be big\nif I'm gonna...
Your muscles are art, right? Then if we\nwant to use them to make NEW art,\nwe gotta use them directly!

I'm a model, not yer damn paintbrush!
Can't ya just sketch me or whatnot?
Here, tell me this don't hit ya right
in yer artsy soul! *flex* *flex*
I want to make something NEWâ€”\nsomething that won't just shake up\nthe art world, but the WHOLE world!
Ugh... How's a guy supposed to turn\ndown talk like that?
Come on! Cover yourself in paint and\ndive onto this paper. Chop chop!
Only way I'M seein' chops anytime\nsoon is if I get this over with...
Fine! This body IS art, so whatever it\ncreates is gonna be prettier than pizza.
Is all the paint finally out of your clothes,\nRanzal?
Perhaps now you will think twice\nbefore using paint to batheâ€”\nfully clothed, no less.
I'm an artist, dammit! Me'n Fleur really\npushed our boundaries today, yeah?
We did manage to make some new art...
But... *sniff* My clothes got caught in the\nsplashback...
*sigh* Yes, you both made quite a mess.\nBut clothes can be cleaned; bring them\nto me once you have changed.
I'll try to cause less damage with my art\nnext time...
I should look for more modelin' gigs...
